DHI inline patch (cassandra 5.0): logback 1.5.x source compat

cassandra 5.0.6 imports ch.qos.logback.core.hook.DelayingShutdownHook, which
logback removed at 1.3+. Replace with DefaultShutdownHook so the bump to
logback 1.5.x in patch/5.0/mvn-dependencies.json (clears CVE-2025-11226 and
the 2024-127xx series) compiles cleanly.

Upstream Cassandra source: https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-5.0.6/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/utils/logging/LogbackLoggingSupport.java
Build wiring: image/cassandra/patch/5.0/mvn-dependencies.json (DHI)

